# Project Structure Guide

This is a **SvelteKit** project for janburzinski.de - a personal portfolio website.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: SvelteKit 2.x with Svelte 5
- **Language**: TypeScript with strict mode
- **Styling**: CSS with modern features (CSS Grid, Flexbox, animations)
- **Build Tool**: Vite
- **Deployment**: Vercel with Node.js 22.x runtime
- **Analytics**: Vercel Analytics
- **Package Manager**: pnpm
- **Linting**: ESLint + Prettier

## Project Structure
- **Entry Point**: [src/app.html](mdc:web/src/app.html)
- **Main Layout**: [src/routes/+layout.svelte](mdc:web/src/routes/+layout.svelte)
- **Homepage**: [src/routes/+page.svelte](mdc:web/src/routes/+page.svelte)
- **Components**: [src/lib/components/](mdc:web/src/lib/components/)
- **Static Assets**: [static/](mdc:web/static/)
- **Configuration**: [svelte.config.js](mdc:web/svelte.config.js), [vite.config.ts](mdc:web/vite.config.ts)

## Key Features
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach with CSS Grid/Flexbox
- **Dark Theme**: Custom color scheme with #121212 background
- **Animations**: CSS keyframes for smooth transitions
- **SEO Optimized**: Proper meta tags and structured data
- **Performance**: Image optimization with Vercel adapter
- **Analytics**: Multiple tracking solutions integrated

## Routes Structure
- `/` - Homepage with profile and about section
- `/resume` - Professional resume/CV
- `/projekte` - Projects showcase (currently commented out)
- `/kontakt` - Contact information
- `/datenschutz` - Privacy policy (German)
- `/impressum` - Legal notice (German)
- `/sitemap.xml` - SEO sitemap

## Component Architecture
- **Navbar.svelte**: Main navigation with desktop/mobile responsive design
- **Footer.svelte**: Site footer component
- **BackgroundEffect.svelte**: Visual background effects
- **Sidebar.svelte**: Mobile sidebar navigation